{
  "text": "English academic writing is a complex and multi-faceted activity that requires coordinating multiple cognitive skills and knowledge to orchestrate writing processes such as facilitating goal setting, problem-solving, and strategically managing memory resources (Allen & McNamara, 2017; Flower & Hayes, 1981).",
